  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check + Rigor Declaration">
      Output: "đź”’ RIGOR LEVEL: FULL â€” chat-agent core cutover + NFR-01 binding + binding cutover of hardcoded text". Read project CLAUDE.md + spec.md FR-03/04 + NFR-01/10/13.
